cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SY

This paper discusses the issue of catastrophic forgetting in deep neural networks and proposes a training technique that leverages metaplasticity models to mitigate this problem. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also presents experimental results and theoretical analysis, which suggest that it could be relevant to sub-categories such as cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
